    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Week-2-lt-2020-07-20-2020-07-26-gt"><a href="#Week-2-lt-2020-07-20-2020-07-26-gt" class="headerlink" title="Week 2 &lt;2020.07.20 - 2020.07.26&gt;"></a>Week 2 &lt;2020.07.20 - 2020.07.26&gt;</h1><h2 id="护网杯-2018-easy-tornado"><a href="#护网杯-2018-easy-tornado" class="headerlink" title="[护网杯 2018]easy_tornado"></a>[护网杯 2018]easy_tornado</h2><h2 id="极客大挑战-2019-Havefun"><a href="#极客大挑战-2019-Havefun" class="headerlink" title="[极客大挑战 2019]Havefun"></a>[极客大挑战 2019]Havefun</h2><p>过程很简单，打开网页查看源代码：</p>
